## Stitch UI Design

Used Google Stitch to generate 2 premium screen designs, then adapted them into React components:

- **Gradient hero headers** with decorative circles and blurred overlays
- **Stat cards** with gradient icon badges and corner decorations
- **Company avatar badges** (first letter, gradient fill)
- **Dot-prefixed status chips** with semantic colors
- **Spring animations** on table rows and job cards
- **Gradient CTA buttons** with box-shadow accents
- **Elevated modal headers** with color-matched gradients (blue=apply, purple=refer)

