## Edge Cases Handled

| Check | Behavior |
|---|---|
| Profile incomplete | ❌ Blocked from apply/refer |
| Job closed / past deadline | ❌ Blocked from apply/refer |
| Duplicate application | ❌ One per student per job |
| Self-referral | ❌ Same email match blocked |
| Duplicate referral email | ❌ Per job uniqueness |
| Max referrals exceeded | ❌ Count enforced at API level |
| Eligibility at apply time | ✅ Re-checked server-side |
| Post-apply eligibility change | ✅ Does NOT invalidate existing application |
